platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With Pulitzer Prize–winning coverage, provocative op-eds, in-depth video docs, and award-winning podcasts, The New York Times expands your understanding of the world. Get alerts for breaking news as well as updates for your favorite coverage areas, like politics, arts, fashion, travel, and science.
